directly and the Jew will vote for a black in a second,'' Mason
said. ``Jews are sick with complexes. They feel guilty for the
black predicament as if the Jews caused it. Jews have always
marched for the blacks. Jews have always supported all their
hospitals, their causes.
   ``The Jews are constantly giving millions of dollars to the
black people. Have you ever heard of a black person giving a
quarter to a Jew?'' Mason asked.
   ``There are plenty of poor Jews in the world. ... I'm not saying
blacks should be giving to the Jews, but Jews don't owe anything to
blacks.''
