<HEAD>North Says War On Drugs Takes More Than Just Saying 'No'</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By W. DALE NELSON</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Oliver L. North, performing community service
in a Washington area drug program as part of his Iran-Contra
