<DATELINE>STOCKHOLM, Sweden (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A district court sentenced a British
soccer fan to 10 months' jail Wednesday for severely beating two
Swedes this month when the countries were competing to qualify for
the World Cup, Swedish radio reported.
   The 21-year-old Briton, who was arrested Sept. 2, will be
expelled after he has served his time and will be barred from
Sweden for 10 years, the radio said.
   His identity was withheld in line with Swedish press regulations.
