<HEAD>Wheat Futures Higher, Corn Lower</HEAD>
<DATELINE>CHICAGO (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Wheat futures prices were mainly higher, corn
prices drifted lower and soybean futures were mixed at the close
Wednesday on the Chicago Board of Trade.
